                "",
                "#doi:10.1088/0954-3899/41/10/105104"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "3CPRIMP"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The 40Ca12+ beam with a typical",
                "intensity of 9E11 ions/s was delivered by the sector",
                "focusing cyclotron of the Heavy Ion Research Facility",
                "in Lanzhou (HIRFL), China. The beam energy at the",
                "center of the target was estimated to be 193 MeV and",
                "the effective irradiation time was 24 hours."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The natural lutetium targets, 175Lu (abundance is",
                "less than 97.4%), 176Lu (abundance is less than 2.6%)",
                "and impurities, with a thickness of 500 ug/cm2 were",
                "evaporated onto 40 ug/cm2 carbon backing foils."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Four silicon avalanche photodiodes mounted at",
                "+-30 degree and +-45 degree with respect to the",
                "incident beam direction were used to monitor the beam",
                "intensity via measuring the scattered projectiles."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The evaporation residues were implanted",
                "into three 300 um thick position sensitive silicon",
                "detectors (PSSDs) abreast installed at the focal",
                "plane of the separator. Each PSSD, with an active",
                "area 50 x 50 mm2, was divided into 16 vertical strips",
                "in the front face. Eight non-position sensitive",
                "silicon detectors of similar type were mounted around",
                "the PSSDs, forming a box of the silicon detector (Si-",
                "box) open from the front side."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MWPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " In order to distinguish the alpha-decay events",
                "from the implantation events, a multi-wire",
                "proportional counter was mounted 15 cm upstream from",
                "the PSSDs."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The evaporation residues (ERs) produced in this",
                "reaction were identified by their characteristic",
                "alpha-decay properties, based on the energy-position-",
                "time correlation measurement."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
